<h1>Event cancelled: <%= @event_name %></h1>

<p>Unfortunately, <strong><%= @store_name %></strong> has cancelled this event, so your order will not be fulfilled.</p>

<% if @reason %>
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p><strong>A note from the baker:</strong></p>
    <p><%= @reason %></p>
  </div>
<% end %>

<p>No action is needed on your end. We're sorry for the inconvenience.</p>

<p>
  Thanks for supporting local bakers!<br>
  — The LocalBaker Team
</p>
